Text:
Superb! Thanks!

But is the 10th song supposed to cut-off like that? (mere 57 seconds and it seems to be building up).
Couldn't tell you why they decided to do it, but yes, they intentionally chose to cut-off the track abruptly like that.
Downloading while I wait for the $86 (with shipping) Limited Edition Vinyl+CD collection that I bought last week. These boys be so good they deserve all your monies! (Please support the artist, yo!)
